# Real-Time Notification Flow

Flow:

1. Customer creates booking
2. Queue job dispatched
3. Nearby plumbers resolved
4. Notification broadcasted
5. Plumber receives popup instantly
6. First accepted plumber gets assignment lock
7. Others receive "booking already taken"

Implement:
- Redis atomic locks
- race condition prevention
- optimistic locking

